Story* 
Once upon a time in a forest there live a monkey who resided on a berry tree,which was on a banlk of a river. And in that river 
lived crocodile and his wife.....
One day the crocodile came to the banks of the river and rested under the tree. 
I kind-hearted monkey offered him some berries. 
The crocodile came back the next day for more berries as he loved them . As days passed by the crocodile and the monkey 
became good friends. 
